trans-unit.source: Identifies the integer properties of a visual style element.
trans-unit.target: 識別屬性的整數的視覺化樣式項目。

trans-unit.source: The IntegerProperty enumeration represents a set of integer properties that describe visual style elements.
trans-unit.target: IntegerProperty 列舉，代表一組整數屬性，描述視覺化樣式項目。

trans-unit.source: The IntegerProperty values are used as an argument in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetInteger%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to specify which property value to retrieve for the element that the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer> currently represents.
trans-unit.target: IntegerProperty 值當做引數用於<xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetInteger%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法，以指定要擷取項目的的屬性值，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer>目前代表。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetInteger%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
